text: COURT OF AUDITORS Special Report No 30/2016 ‘The effectiveness of EU support to priority sectors in Honduras’ (2017/C 10/03) The European Court of Auditors hereby informs you that Special Report No 30/2016 ‘The effectiveness of EU support to priority sectors in Honduras’ has just been published. The report can be accessed for consultation or downloading on the European Court of Auditors’ website: http://eca.europa.eu or on EU Bookshop: https://bookshop.europa.eu C 10/8 EN Official Journal of the European Union 13.1.2017
